<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .content h2 {
        color: #007bff;
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-top: 0;
      }
      .content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .order-details {
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        width: 100%;
      }
      .order-details th,
      .order-details td {
        padding: 10px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      .order-details th {
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        text-align: left;
      }
      .order-details td {
        text-align: left;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .footer p {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .footer a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Your eLearning Order is Confirmed!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>And we're just as excited as you are.</p>
        <h2>Here's what you ordered:</h2>
        <table class="order-details">
          <tr>
            <td>Order #:<%= order._id %></td>
            <td>Order Date<%= order.date %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <table class="order-details">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Item</th>
              <th>Qty</th>
              <th>Cost</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
        </table>
        <table class="order-details">
          <tr>
            <th>Subtotal:</th>
            <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Total:</th>
            <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          If you have any questions, please contact our support team at
          <a href="mailto:support@becodemy.com">support@becodemy.com</a>
        </p>
        <p>&copy; 2023 eLearning. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

